ViewObject.Name: CLMInvoiceHomeVO
ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT xlpit.*, DECODE (xlpit.attached_file_name, NULL, 'Once Upload the Attachment and It will go for approval', xlpit.invoice_wf_status ) invoice_status_process FROM xxsify_CLM_payment_invoice_tab xlpit WHERE invoice_type = 'STANDARD' AND stg_batch_id IS NOT NULL
